reviewText: It looks like someone sat in front of a tv and videotaped old movies. Video is jumpy. But that's what it's like to watch some of these old films.
These vintage "golden age" TV productions bring some of Hollywood's biggest stars to early Television.  Delightful.
I love old Christmas stories/movies. These old TV episodes were part of my memories. The magi movie is historical; a learning experience.
Great for nostalgia and love those true classic actors.  There is something about the pure wholeness of those old movies and very fine actors.

The cover of the DVD displays better quality than the actual DVD - The sound and picture quality is not as good as other movies we've viewed of the same/similar era.Rare Christmas TV Classics - Volume 2 Story content very disappointing in all four stories.
Thanks and God Bless y'all and your families, friends, etc... for this much appreciated product.
A real nice DVD the way  Christmas used to be, fun and warm stories.
